<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Challenge Update Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333333;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      .highlight {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #0056b3;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888888;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <p>Hi {{RecipientName}},</p>

      <p>
        Heads up! The challenge 
        <strong>“{{ChallengeName}}”</strong> 
        has been updated by <strong>{{UpdatedBy}}</strong> 
        by <strong>TruPreneurs.AI</strong>. ✨
      </p>

      <p>
        Check out the changes, explore the updated details, 
        and keep pushing your ideas forward! 💡
      </p>

      <p>Best Regards,<br/>TruPreneurs.AI</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} TruPreneurs.AI. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
